Module kivakit.serialization.core
Package com.telenav.kivakit.serialization.core

Interface SerializationSessionReadWrite

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SerializationSession
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    KryoSerializationSession
    public interface SerializationSessionReadWrite
    Unversioned primitive read and write methods. Prefer the automatically versioned SerializationSession.read() and SerializationSession.write(VersionedObject) methods whenever possible.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
    See Also:
    SerializationSession
